text: Maha Haddioui, Arabic: ماها الحديوي , (born May 15, 1988 in Casablanca) is a Moroccan female golfer. She has been a professional since 2011. Haddioui plays on the Ladies European Tour and obtained second last place at the 2016 Summer Olympics.
